FBIS4-15661 "drsov069_b_94020" FBIS-SOV-94-069 Daily Report 8 Apr 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Military, Space & Nuclear Issues Defense Ministry Denies Air Defense Troops Disbanding Defense Ministry Denies Air Defense Troops Disbanding LD0804215594 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1325 GMT 8 Apr 94 LD0804215594 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Russian BFN [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Anatoliy Yurkin] [Text] Moscow, 8 Apr -- The Air Defense Troops will continue to fulfill the tasks before them, remaining an arm of Russia's Armed Forces, a spokesmen at the Russian Ministry of Defense told the ITAR-TASS correspondent, denying press reports about the disbanding of the Air Defense Troops. It emerges from the explanation that structural reorganization is nearing completion in the Air Defense Troops. The number of personnel has been cut here, as in other arms of the Russian Armed Forces.
